### Coze 原生 developer：connector bind
POST {{host}}/api/draftbot/bind/connector
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "space_id": "{{workspaceId}}",
  "bot_id": "1",
  "connector_id": "2001",
  "connector_info": {
    "endpoint_url": "https://example.test/webhook",
    "api_key": "demo-key",
    "share_link": "https://example.test/share/bot-1"
  },
  "agent_type": 0
}

### Coze 原生 developer：connector auth state
GET {{host}}/api/user/auth/connector_state?connector_id=3001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

