}

### Coze 原生 developer：publish draftbot
POST {{host}}/api/draftbot/publish
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "space_id": "{{workspaceId}}",
  "bot_id": "1",
  "publish_id": "compat-publish-1",
  "history_info": "compat publish",
  "connectors": {
    "1001": {},
    "2001": {
      "endpoint_url": "https://example.test/webhook",
      "api_key": "demo-key",
      "share_link": "https://example.test/share/bot-1"
    }
  }
}

